data.description: This gorgeous property in beautiful First Creek Village feels brand new with white exterior stucco and professional landscaping! This beautiful 3 bed/2.5 bath home is situated just minutes away from the Denver International Airport, Gaylord Rockies Resort, dining, shopping, parks and much more!!! Your loved ones will enjoy the spacious open floor plan of this Oakwood Platte Model Home that features a backyard that is perfect for family gatherings with lots of stamped concrete! The open kitchen to the dining area provides all the space you need for entertaining.  Come and Look at this beauty....Don't miss out!
